'''劳伦·欧帕尔·博伯特'''（{{lang-en|Lauren Opal Boebert}}，{{bd|1986年|12月15日}}<ref name="ColoSun09142020"/>）是一位[[美国|美国]][[政治家|政治家]]、[[商人|商人]]、[[美国枪支政策|枪支权利]]活动家，也是{{le|科罗拉多州第三国会选区|Colorado's 3rd congressional district}}的[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]议员。她是众议院首位代表科罗拉多州第三国会选区的女性。

博伯特在[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]][[赖夫尔_(科罗拉多州)|赖夫尔]]拥有一家名为射手烧烤（{{lang|en|Shooters Grill}}）的餐厅，并鼓励员工[[美国公开持武权|公开携带枪支]]。在{{le|2020年科罗拉多州美国众议院选举|2020 United States House of Representatives elections in Colorado|2020年国会众议院选举}}中，她作为[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]人参加了{{le|科罗拉多州第三国会选区|Colorado's 3rd congressional district}}的选举，并在初选中击败了现任国会议员[[斯科特·蒂普顿|斯科特·蒂普顿]]。正式选举中，博伯特击败了前[[科罗拉多州众议院|州众议院]]议员{{le|黛安·米奇·布什|Diane Mitsch Bush}}，赢得了选举。博伯特曾表示支持[[极右翼|极右翼]][[阴谋论|阴谋论]][[匿名者Q|匿名者Q]]<ref>{{Cite web|author=Bridget Bowman|date=2020-06-30|title=Colorado Rep. Scott Tipton ousted in primary by gun rights activist|url=https://www.rollcall.com/2020/06/30/colorado-rep-scott-tipton-ousted-in-primary-by-gun-rights-activist/|dead-url=no|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-11-13|website=Roll Call|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|author=Jesse Paul|date=2020-06-30|title=Lauren Boebert beats U.S. Rep. Scott Tipton in Republican primary|url=https://coloradosun.com/2020/06/30/lauren-boebert-scott-tipton-colorado/|dead-url=no|archive-url=|archive-date=|accessdate=2020-11-13|website=The Colorado Sun|language=en}}</ref>，不过她后来表示她不是匿名者Q的追随者<ref name="FOX31" />。

==早年生活==
博伯特于1986年12月15日出生于[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[阿尔塔蒙特斯普林斯_(佛罗里达州)|阿尔塔蒙特斯普林斯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://thehill.com/new-members-guide-2020/527747-rep-elect-lauren-boebert-r-colo-03 |title = Rep.-elect Lauren Boebert (R-Colo.-03)|website=The Hill|date = 2020-11-30 |language = en|accessdate =2021-01-13}}</ref><ref name="ColoSun09142020">{{Cite web |url = https://coloradosun.com/2020/09/14/lauren-boebert-congress-guns-trump/ |title = How Lauren Boebert rose from unknown to a candidate for Congress to someone in Donald Trump’s orbit|website=Colorado Sun |author = Lofholm, Nancy|date = 2020-09-14 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref>。12岁时，她和家人搬到[[丹佛|丹佛]]的{{le|蒙贝洛 (丹佛)|Montbello, Denver|蒙贝洛}}社区，后来搬到科罗拉多州的[[奥罗拉_(科罗拉多州)|奥罗拉]]，2003年在[[赖夫尔_(科罗拉多州)|赖夫尔]]定居下来<ref name="JWingDenPost07272020"/><ref>{{Cite web|last=Rice|first=Heidi|title=Regional: Shooters in Rifle serves a big helping of Second Amendment|url=https://www.postindependent.com/news/regional-shooters-in-rifle-serves-a-big-helping-of-second-amendment/|date=2014-07-14|access-date=2021-01-13|work=Glenwood Springs Post Independent|language=en-US}}</ref>。

博伯特说，她的父母投票给[[民主党_(美国)|民主党人]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://coloradosun.com/2020/09/16/lauren-boebert-backstory-details-durango-herald/ |title = Lauren Boebert discusses, defends her backstory during Durango visit|website=The Durango Herald |author = Armijo, Patrick|date = 2020-09-16 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{Cite web|last=Kim|first=Caitlyn|date=2020-07-01|title=Who Is Lauren Boebert?|url=https://www.cpr.org/2020/07/01/who-is-lauren-boebert/|access-date=2021-01-13|website=Colorado Public Radio|language=en}}</ref>，他们生活在丹佛的贫困中，她的母亲在那里领取[[社会福利|福利]]。2001年，博伯特14岁时，她的母亲注册成为[[共和党_(美国)|共和党人]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.gjsentinel.com/news/western_colorado/boeberts-democratic-upbringing-questioned/article_599f9890-f867-11ea-a66d-836e16473c98.html |title = Boebert's Democratic upbringing questioned|website=Daily Sentinel |author = Ashby, Charles|date = 2020-09-21 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref>。博伯特认为，她15岁时在[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]餐厅的第一份工作改变了她对政府援助是否必要的看法<ref name="JWingDenPost07272020"/><ref name="Westworld01142020">{{Cite web|url=https://www.westword.com/news/lauren-boebert-takes-aim-at-colorado-congressman-scott-tipton-11575424|title=Lauren Boebert on Her Fully Loaded Campaign Against Scott Tipton|first=Michael|last=Roberts|date=2020-01-14|website=Westword|access-date=2021-01-13}}</ref> 。

博伯特高中退学，因为她有了一个孩子。之后她在赖夫尔的一家麦当劳担任管理职务。后来她获得了[[普通教育发展证书|普通教育发展证书]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://durangoherald.com/articles/339152 |title = Lauren Boebert defends her past during Durango visit|website=Durango Herald |author = Armijo, Patrick|date = 2020-09-15 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref>。接下来她在一家[[油井|天然气钻井]]公司申请了一份工作，成为了一名[[管道运输|管道工]]，作为建造维护管道和泵站的团队成员<ref name="FXNws11252020">{{Cite web |url = https://www.foxnews.com/politics/colo-rep-elect-lauren-boebert-plans-thanksgiving-funeral-for-dead-turkey-in-defiance-of-local-guidelines|title = Rep.-elect Lauren Boebert plans Thanksgiving 'funeral' for dead turkey in defiance of Colorado guidelines|website=FOX News |author = Schultz, Marisa|date =  |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref>。

==事业==
===生意===
[[File:Lauren_Boebert.JPG|left]]
2013年，博伯特被解雇后，和丈夫在[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]的[[赖夫尔_(科罗拉多州)|赖夫尔]]开设了射手烧烤餐厅（{{lang|en|Shooters Grill}}）。附近的一条巷子里有人遭到袭击后，博伯特获得了{{le|隐蔽携带|Concealed carry}}许可证，并开始鼓励餐厅服务员[[美国公开持武权|公开携带武器]]<ref name="heraldtimes">{{Cite web|last=Turner|first=Nikki|url=https://www.theheraldtimes.com/shooters-grill-owner-enters-us-house-race/rio-blanco-county/|title=Shooters Grill owner enters US House race|date=2020-01-03|work=Rio Blanco Herald Times|access-date=2021-01-13}}</ref><ref name=burgers>{{cite web|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/530154947/?terms=Lauren%2BBoebert|title=Burger with a side arm: Gun-packing service draws spotlight, more customers to Rifle restaurant|first=Rachel|last=Sauer|work=Daily Sentinel|page=1D|date=2014-08-10|access-date=2021-01-13|via=Newspapers.com}}</ref>。2015年，博伯特一家在赖夫尔克里克高尔夫球场（{{lang|en|Rifle Creek Golf Course}}）开设了另一家名为{{lang|en|Putters}}的餐厅<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.postindependent.com/rifle/shooters-makes-transition-from-guns-to-golf-clubs/|title=Shooters makes transition from guns to golf clubs|first=Heidi|last=Rice|work=Glenwood Springs Post Independent|date=2015-03-12|access-date=2021-01-13}}</ref>。

2020年5月中旬，在[[COVID-19大流行|COVID-19大流行]]期间，博伯特违反了该州的“[[居家令|居家令]]”规定，重新开放了射手烧烤餐厅，以供堂食<ref>{{Cite web|last=Corey|first=Calvin|date=2020-05-13|title="I’m not going to wait on the government to tell me what to do." Lauren Boebert says Shooter's Grill in Rifle is open for business|url=https://www.nbc11news.com/content/news/Lauren-Boebert--says-shes-opened-Shooters-Grill-in-Rifle--570410401.html|access-date=2021-01-13|publisher=KKCO}}</ref>。尽管她收到了[[加菲尔德县_(科罗拉多州)|加菲尔德县]]的停业命令，但博伯特说她不会结束自己的生意<ref>{{Cite web|last=Sieg|first=Stina|date=2020-05-14|title=Shooters Grill In Rifle Defies Cease-And-Desist Order|url=https://www.cpr.org/2020/05/14/rifle-restaurant-shooters-grill-defies-a-cease-and-desist-order-to-keep-serving-diners/|access-date=2021-01-13|website=Colorado Public Radio|language=en}}</ref>。次日，她把桌子搬到了外面的人行道和停车位上<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-05-15|title=Shooters Grill Moves Tables Outside To Serve Customers After Cease & Desist Order|url=https://denver.cbslocal.com/2020/05/15/shooters-grill-rifle-restaurant-cease-desist-coronavirus/|access-date=2021-01-13|website=CBSN Denver|language=en-US}}</ref>。次日，加菲尔德县暂停了她的食品许可证<ref>{{Cite web|last=Tabachnik|first=Sam|date=2020-05-16|title=Shooters Grill in Rifle has food license suspended, owner says|url=https://www.denverpost.com/2020/05/16/shooters-grill-rifle-license-suspended/|access-date=2021-01-13|website=The Denver Post|language=en-US}}</ref>。到5月底，州政府允许餐馆以50%的容量重新营业，加菲尔德县取消了临时限制令<ref>{{Cite web|last=Stroud|first=John|date=2020-05-27|title=Court case against Shooters Grill dismissed, but license still suspended as county, owner negotiate reopening|url=https://www.aspentimes.com/news/regional/court-case-against-shooters-grill-dismissed-but-license-still-suspended-as-county-owner-negotiate-reopening/|access-date=2021-01-13|website=www.aspentimes.com|language=en-US}}</ref>。

===枪支权利倡导者===
2019年9月，博伯特参与了[[持枪权|枪支权利]]活动，在2020年总统竞选期间，他在[[奥罗拉_(科罗拉多州)|奥罗拉]][[市政厅|市政厅]]会议上对{{le|贝托·奥罗克|Beto O'Rourke}}提出的{{le|枪支回购计划|Gun buyback program}}提出挑战，并说：“见鬼，不，你不会拿走我们的枪。”<ref>{{Cite web|last=Boyd|first=Shaun|url=https://denver.cbslocal.com/2019/09/20/beto-orourke-aurora-colorado-buyback-ar-15-ak-47-semi-automatic/|title=Colorado Woman Challenges Beto O'Rourke's Plan For Buyback Of AR-15s, AK-47s|work=CBS Local|date=2019-09-20|access-date=2021-01-13}}</ref>她在[[阿斯彭_(科罗拉多州)|阿斯彭]]{{le|市议会|City council}}的一次会议上反对[[枪支管制|枪支管制]]措施<ref>{{Cite web|last=Sackariason|first=Carolyn|date=2019-09-24|title=Garfield County gun advocates take aim at Aspen’s proposed prohibition of deadly weapons in city buildings|url=https://www.postindependent.com/news/gun-advocates-take-aim-at-aspens-proposed-prohibition-of-deadly-weapons-in-city-buildings/|access-date=2021-01-13|work=Glenwood Springs Post Independent}}</ref>。2020年11月，博伯特说她计划在[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]][[美国国会大厦|国会大厦]]担任议员期间携带枪支<ref name="FXNws11252020"/><ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-01-05|title=Republican Lauren Boebert vows to carry handgun to Congress|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-55540155|access-date=2021-01-13}}</ref>。

2021年1月，博伯特制作了一则广告，宣布她有权在[[美国国会大厦|美国国会大厦]]和华盛顿街头携带[[格洛克手枪|格洛克手枪]]。这则广告显示，博伯特把格洛克手枪绑在臀部，步行穿过[[国会山|国会山]]，接近联邦大楼然后穿过小巷。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/legal-issues/boebert-capitol-guns/2021/01/04/a59f70f8-4e9d-11eb-83e3-322644d82356_story.html |title = In ad, lawmaker vows to carry her Glock around D.C. and on Hill|website=Washington Post |author = Flynn, Meagan|date = 2021-01-04 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://nypost.com/2021/01/05/rep-lauren-boebert-loads-gun-walks-around-dc-in-new-video/ |title = Rep. Lauren Boebert releases video of herself walking around DC with gun|website=New York Post |author = Eustachewich, Lia|date = 2021-01-05 |language = en|accessdate =2021-01-13}}</ref>

==美国众议院==
===选举===
====2020年====
2019年12月，博伯特宣布在[[2020年美国众议院选举|2020年美国众议院选举]]中参选{{le|科罗拉多州第三国会选区|Colorado's 3rd congressional district}}，首先是在[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]][[初选|初选]]中挑战现任议员[[斯科特·蒂普顿|斯科特·蒂普顿]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cpr.org/2020/06/22/rep-scott-tipton-faces-a-primary-challenger-who-questions-his-record-and-whether-hes-trump-enough/|title=Lauren Boebert Questions If Rep. Scott Tipton Is Trump Enough|first=Caitlyn|last=Kim|website=Colorado Public Radio|date=2020-06-22|access-date=2021-01-13}}</ref>。在竞选期间，博伯特批评了[[亚历山德里娅·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯|亚历山德里娅·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯]]和其他“{{le|小队 (美国国会)|The Squad (United States Congress)|小队}}”成员，将自己定位为奥卡西奥-科尔特斯的保守派替代者<ref name="RollCall07012020">{{Cite web |url = https://www.rollcall.com/2020/07/01/lauren-boebert-ran-against-aoc-and-the-squad-and-beat-rep-scott-tipton-in-the-process/ |title = Lauren Boebert ran against AOC and the ‘squad,’ and beat Rep. Scott Tipton in the process|website=Roll Call |author = Bowman, Bridget|date = 2020-07-01 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref><ref name="auto1">{{Cite web|last=Panetta|first=Grace|date=2020-06-30|title=GOP Congressman Scott Tipton was defeated by right-wing primary challenger Lauren Boebert in Colorado's 3rd congressional district|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/lauren-boebert-defeats-scott-tipton-colorado-third-district-primary-live-results-2020-6|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Business Insider}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|first=Megan |last=Tackett|date=2019-12-10|title=Owner of Shooters Grill challenges Tipton in primary|url=https://www.aspendailynews.com/news/owner-of-shooters-grill-challenges-tipton-in-primary/article_10f1436c-1afc-11ea-bf84-13041980da46.html|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Aspen Daily News|language=en}}</ref>。[[丹佛大学|丹佛大学]]政治学教授塞思·马斯克特提出，博伯特此举是希望通过激起共和党选民对奥卡西奥-科尔特斯等人的愤怒，在漫长的选举周期中激励他们参加初选<ref name="RollCall07012020"/>。

博伯特批评了蒂普顿的投票记录，她说这并没有反映第三选区的情况<ref name="KimNPR06222020"/>。初选前，总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]支持蒂普顿，在竞选期间，博伯特将蒂普顿定性为不支持特朗普<ref name="RollCall07012020"/>。她指责蒂普顿支持大赦无证移民，投票支持H.R.5038，即2019年的《农业劳动力现代化法案》（{{lang|en|Farm Workforce Modernization Act of 2019}}），并称该法案有一项规定与公民身份相关，还为无证农业工人提供住房资金<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.gjsentinel.com/news/western_colorado/republican-candidate-and-owner-of-gun-toting-grill-accuses-tipton-of-supporting-amnesty-bill/article_5cc12a26-30a7-11ea-875c-97c44c2b1bf5.html |title = Republican candidate and owner of gun-toting grill accuses Tipton of supporting amnesty bill|website=The Daily Sentineling-amnesty-bill/article_5cc12a26-30a7-11ea-875c-97c44c2b1bf5.html |author = Ashby, Charles|date = 2020-07-01 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref>。博伯特批评了蒂普顿为{{le|工资保障计划|Paycheck Protection Program}}提供资金的努力，说他没有为该计划争取到足够多的资金，该计划在两周内就花光了资金<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://durangoherald.com/articles/321975 |title = Restaurant owner gets top line on Republican primary ballot|website=Durango Herald |author = Armijo, Patrick|date = 2020-04-20 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref>。在6月30日初选时，博伯特在与蒂普顿的竞选期间总共筹到了15万美元<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.coloradopolitics.com/2020-election/national-gop-congressional-group-names-lauren-boebert-to-young-guns-program/article_909ea5ee-d81d-11ea-9a1a-3b59c99eaf15.html |title=National GOP congressional group names Lauren Boebert to 'Young Guns' program |last=Luning |first=Earnest |date=2020-08-06 |website=Colorado Politics|publisher=Clarity Media Corporation |location=Denver, Colorado|access-date=2021-01-15 }}</ref>。

6月30日，博伯特以54.6%的得票率赢得了共和党提名<ref>{{Cite web|last=LeBlanc|first=Paul|date=2020-07-01|title=Trump-backed five-term Republican lawmaker loses primary to challenger who praised QAnon conspiracy|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/06/30/politics/scott-tipton-loses-lauren-boebert-colorado/index.html|access-date=2021-01-15|publisher=CNN}}</ref>。她是民主党众议员{{le|韦恩·阿斯皮纳尔|Wayne N. Aspinall}}输给艾伦·默森后48年来首位击败在任[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]国会众议员的初选挑战者<ref name="DWebbGJS07122020">{{Cite web |url = https://www.gjsentinel.com/news/western_colorado/around-boebert-s-hometown-her-victory-greeted-by-gop-with-joy-apprehension/article_73dc8b44-c2c2-11ea-b2b3-a7f34a8ab1f8.html |title = Around Boebert’s hometown, her victory greeted by GOP with joy, apprehension|website=Grand Junction Daily Sentinel |author = Webb, Dennis|date = 2020-07-12 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://gazette.com/premium/lauren-boebert-rockets-to-fame-and-controversy-in-primary-upset-in-colorado-congressional-race/article_e25ba5bf-428c-5ece-833a-046f9324004d.html |title = Lauren Boebert rockets to fame — and controversy — in primary upset in Colorado congressional race|website=Colorado Springs Gazette |author = Luning, Ernest|date = 2020-07-04 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref>。博伯特承诺在众议院就职后将加入{{le|自由核心小组|Freedom Caucus}}<ref name="KimNPR06222020">{{Cite web|last=Kim|first=Caitlyn|date=2020-06-22|title=Lauren Boebert Questions If Rep. Scott Tipton Is Trump Enough|url=https://www.cpr.org/2020/06/22/rep-scott-tipton-faces-a-primary-challenger-who-questions-his-record-and-whether-hes-trump-enough/|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Colorado Public Radio|language=en}}</ref>。

博伯特在11月的大选中面对[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]前州众议员、[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]][[斯廷博特斯普林斯_(科罗拉多州)|斯廷博特斯普林斯]]退休社会学教授{{le|黛安·米奇·布什|Diane Mitsch Bush}}。博伯特说她相信米奇·布什的纲领是“更多的政府控制”，米奇·布什有一个“社会主义议程”<ref name="DWebbGJS07122020" />。7月下旬，博伯特被认为是领先者<ref name="JWingDenPost07272020">{{cite news |last=Wingerter |first=Justin |date=2020-07-27 |title=Lauren Boebert beat a Colorado congressman. Is she the next GOP star? |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2020/07/26/lauren-boebert-colorado-3rd-district-gop-trump/ |work=Denver Post|location=Denver, Colorado |access-date=2021-01-15|quote=The political novice is now the front-runner to win Nov. 3 over Democrat Diane Mitsch Bush in this Republican-leaning district.}}</ref>。由[[迈克尔·布隆伯格|迈克尔·布隆伯格]]领导的倾向民主党的众议院多数党政治行动委员会在9月进行的一项调查显示，米奇·布什领先1个百分点<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.westernslopenow.com/news/local-news/local-political-leaders-react-to-a-recent-poll-for-co-district-3/ |title = Local political leaders react to a recent poll for CO District 3|website=Westernslopenow |author = September 21, 2020|date = 2020-09-21 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref>。11月3日，博伯特以51.27%对45.41%击败了米奇·布什。此次选举博伯特筹集了240万美元，米奇·布什筹集了420万美元<ref name="ColoSun11032020">{{Cite web |url = https://coloradosun.com/2020/11/03/lauren-boebert-diane-mitsch-bush-colorado-results/ |title = Lauren Boebert beats Democrat Diane Mitsch Bush in Colorado’s 3rd Congressional District|website=Colorado Sun |date = 2020-11-03 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref>。共和党团体花费了超过500万美元。民主党团体花费了近400万美元<ref name="ColoSun11032020"/>。博伯特把大选的重点放在了枪支权利、能源和宪法上<ref name="FXStabil11092020">{{cite news |title=13 GOP women join the House, dominating congressional elections, making history |url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/13-gop-women-joining-the-house-to-dominate-congressional-elections |date=2020-11-09 |last=Stabile |first=Angelica |publisher=FOX News|access-date=2021-01-15 }}</ref>。

在竞选期间，博伯特在一个支持[[匿名者Q|匿名者Q]]的网络节目中对匿名者Q阴谋论表示支持：“我所听到的关于Q的一切，我希望这是真实的，因为这只意味着美国正在变得越来越强大和更好。”<ref>{{Cite web|last=Robillard|first=Kevin|date=2020-07-01|title=A QAnon Supporter Just Beat A Republican Congressman in Colorado|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/a-qanon-supporter-just-beat-a-republican-congressman-in-colorado_n_5efbfb3fc5b6ca97091685a3|access-date=2021-01-15|website=HuffPost|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Kurtzleben|first=Danielle|date=2020-07-01|title=GOP Candidates Open To QAnon Conspiracy Theory Advance In Congressional Races|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/07/01/885991730/gop-candidates-open-to-qanon-conspiracy-theory-advance-in-congressional-races|access-date=2021-01-15|website=NPR.org|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Peters|first=Cameron|date=2020-07-03|title=The QAnon supporters winning congressional primaries, explained|url=https://www.vox.com/2020/7/3/21309935/qanon-supporters-winning-congressional-primaries-explained|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Vox|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Anderson|first=Jim|last2=Riccardi|first2=Nicholas|last3=Fram|first3=Alan|date=2020-07-02|title=Colorado's GOP U.S. House candidate Lauren Boebert is latest linked to QAnon conspiracy theory|url=https://coloradosun.com/2020/07/01/lauren-boebert-qanon-gop-colorado/|access-date=2021-01-15|website=The Colorado Sun|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Hulse|first=Carl|date=2020-06-30|title=Lauren Boebert, Gun-Rights Activist, Upsets House G.O.P. Incumbent in Colorado|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/30/us/lauren-boebert-colorado.html|access-date=2021-01-15|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>匿名者Q被[[美国联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]列为[[本土恐怖主义|本土恐怖主义]]威胁，并被称为邪教，是一个极右翼阴谋网络<ref>{{cite web|last1=Dickson|first1=E.J.|date=2019-08-02|title=The FBI Declared QAnon a Domestic Terrorism Threat — and Conspiracy Theorists Are Psyched|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-features/qanon-domestic-terrorism-threat-conspiracy-theory-866288/|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Rolling Stone}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=LaFrance|first1=Adrienne|date=2020-05-13|title=The Prophecies of Q: American conspiracy theories are entering a dangerous new phase|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2020/06/qanon-nothing-can-stop-what-is-coming/610567/|access-date=2021-01-15|newspaper=The Atlantic}}</ref>。在2020年7月6日，博伯特谈到匿名者Q时说：“我不是一个追随者。匿名者Q对于各别的人来说代表着很多东西。我以前说的话很含糊。我不喜欢阴谋。我喜欢自由和美国宪法。我不是一个追随者。”<ref name="FOX31">{{Cite web|last=Harsha|first=Keagan|date=2020-07-07|title=Colorado primary winner Lauren Boebert meets President Trump, distances herself from QAnon|url=https://kdvr.com/news/politics/colorado-primary-winner-lauren-boebert-meets-president-trump-distances-herself-from-qanon/|access-date=2020-07-26|website=FOX31 Denver|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Anderson |first1=Jim |last2=Riccardi |first2=Nicholas |last3=Fram |first3=Alan|date=2020-07-02 |title=GOP candidate is latest linked to QAnon conspiracy theory |url=https://apnews.com/e21311e35e7063834222942a1702211b |work=Associated Press |location=New York City |access-date=2021-01-15}}</ref>

===任期===
2021年1月1日，博伯特写信给[[美国众议院议长|众议院议长]][[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]和[[美国众议院政党领导人|众议院少数党领袖]][[凯文·麦卡锡|凯文·麦卡锡]]，这封信由其他国会议员和当选议员签署，要求1967年国会议员免于国会山枪支禁令的法律继续生效，允许他们继续携带枪支。2020年11月，博伯特说她打算在华盛顿特区工作时携带枪支。她收集了其他82名议员的签名，包括[[丹·克伦肖|丹·克伦肖]]、[[吉姆·乔丹_(美国政治人物)|吉姆·乔丹]]、[[莫·布鲁克斯|莫·布鲁克斯]]、[[马奎恩·穆林|马奎恩·穆林]]，以及当选议员{{le|维多利亚·斯巴兹|Victoria Spartz}}和{{le|伊薇特·赫瑞尔|Yvette Herrell}}。在佩洛西颁布了新规则之后，1967年的豁免仍然保留在众议院规则中。<ref>{{cite news |last=Stimson |first=Brie |date=2021-01-03 |title=Colorado congresswoman-elect appears to score win on Capitol gun rights |url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/colorado-congresswoman-elect-appears-to-score-win-on-capitol-gun-rights |work=FOX News |access-date=2021-01-08|quote=Rep.-elect Lauren Boebert, R-Colo., wrote a letter to House leadership Friday, urging them to keep a 1967 rule that exempts lawmakers from a ban on firearms inside the Capitol building.}}</ref>

2021年1月3日，国会议员[[托马斯·马西|托马斯·马西]]与博伯特正式成立了国会{{le|第二修正案核心小组|Second Amendment Caucus}}，两人将在未来至少两年的时间里担任该核心小组联合主席。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://boebert.house.gov/media/press-releases/its-official-congresswoman-lauren-boebert-takes-oath-office|title = It’s Official: Congresswoman Lauren Boebert Takes Oath of Office|website=boebert.house.gov|date = 2021-01-03 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref>

2021年1月5日，博伯特说，1月6日将是共和党的“1776时刻”<ref>{{Cite news|last=Edmondson|first=Catie|last2=Broadwater|first2=Luke|date=2021-01-12|title=Before Capitol Riot, Republican Lawmakers Fanned the Flames|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/11/us/politics/republicans-capitol-riot.html|access-date=2021-01-15|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>。民主党政治家指责她和她的同事[[道格·兰博恩|道格·兰博恩]]在1月6日的[[2021年冲击美国国会大厦事件|2021年冲击美国国会大厦事件]]中“协助煽动暴力”<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.coloradopolitics.com/denver-gazette/elected-officials-and-others-demand-reps-boebert-lamborn-resign-over-wednesdays-washington-d-c-riot/article_3a2a74b8-5135-11eb-abdf-9f74bb3076d2.html |title = State and local Democrats, others demand Reps. Boebert, Lamborn resign over Wednesday's Washington, D.C. riot|website=Colorado Politics |author = Goodland, Marianne|date = 2021-01-07 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.9news.com/article/news/politics/officials-boebert-lamborn-washington-dc-d-c-riot/73-da19968c-b5ca-44d9-8e29-d1a80f06d66d |publisher=KUSA|title=Elected officials and others demand Reps. Boebert, Lamborn resign over Wednesday's Washington, D.C. riot |access-date=2021-01-10 |date=2021-01-07 |first=Marianne |last=Goodland}}</ref>。许多民主党政治家、[[普韦布洛_(科罗拉多州)|普韦布洛]]居民<ref>{{cite news |last1=Willard |first1=Heather |title=Anti-Lauren Boebert group stages rally outside district offices in Pueblo |url=https://www.chieftain.com/story/news/2021/01/08/puebloans-call-lauren-boeberts-resignation-removal/6599800002/ |access-date=2021-01-15 |work=Pueblo Chieftain |date=2021-01-08}}</ref>和[[杜兰戈_(科罗拉多州)|杜兰戈]]居民<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://durangoherald.com/articles/359868 |title = Durango protesters decry U.S. Rep. Lauren Boebert’s rhetoric|website=Durango Herald |author = Purcell, John|date = 2021-01-08 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-15}}</ref>要求她辞职，因为她在推特上发布佩洛西的位置信息<ref>{{cite web |title=QAnon congresswoman who live-tweeted Nancy Pelosi's location to rioters now facing calls for arrest |url=https://www.salon.com/2021/01/11/qanon-congresswoman-who-live-tweeted-nancy-pelosis-location-to-rioters-now-facing-calls-for-arrest_partner/ |website=Salon |access-date=2021-01-15 |language=en |date=2021-01-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Graziosi|first=Graig|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-election-2020/qanon-lauren-boebert-nancy-pelosi-capitol-riot-b1785663.html|title='QAnon Congresswoman' Lauren Boebert faces calls to resign after tweeting information about Nancy Pelosi during Capitol riot|work=The Independent|location=London|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-15}}</ref>。1月12日，当博伯特穿过新安装的国会山金属探测器时，探测器响了，她拒绝把包交出检查，随后进入国会大厦。博伯特称金属探测器“只是议长佩洛西的又一个政治噱头”<ref>{{cite news |last1=Brodsky |first1=Rachel |title=Congresswoman Lauren Boebert ‘was in stand-off on Capitol Hill after refusing bag search’ |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/lauren-boebert-capitol-hill-metal-detectors-b1786385.html |work=The Independent|location=London|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Wingerter |first1=Justin |title=Lauren Boebert causes holdup at U.S. House security, refuses to turn over her bag |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2021/01/12/lauren-boebert-guns-congress-security-stop/ |publisher=Denver Post |date=2021-01-12|accessdate=2021-01-15}}</ref>。事件发生后，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》对博伯特的报道称她是“极右翼”和“阴谋论者”<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Rogers|first1=Katie|last2=Philipps|first2=Dave|date=2021-01-14|title=A Republican Lawmaker for Whom the Spectacle Is the Point|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/13/us/politics/lauren-boebert-republican.html|access-date=2021-01-15|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>。

