==政治立场==
===预算===
在2020年的竞选活动中，博伯特承诺，如果成功当选众议员，她将不会支持任何导致额外债务的联邦预算<ref name="DetFP07012020"/>。她支持[[美国宪法|美国宪法]]的{{le|平衡预算宪法修正案|Balanced budget amendment}}<ref>{{Citation |last=Wiggins |first=Mike |date=2020-08-05 |title=Boebert fires up Ouray County crowd |publisher=Ouray County Plaindealer |publication-place=Ridgway, Colorado |url=https://www.ouraynews.com/news/boebert-fires-ouray-county-crowd |access-date=2021-01-12|quote=She did say she thinks federal spending is “out of control” and blamed both Democrats and Republicans for that. If elected, she said she would introduce a balanced-budget amendment.}}</ref>。

