博伯特支持“以上所有能源”（{{lang|en|all-of-above energy}}）政策，即开发和利用各种资源来满足能源需求。资源包括[[不可再生能源|不可再生资源]]（如[[原油|原油]]）和[[可再生能源|可再生资源]]（如[[太阳能|太阳能]]）。<ref name="ColoPubRadio08242020">{{Cite web |url = https://www.cpr.org/2020/08/24/the-race-is-on-colorados-3rd-district-candidates-stump-from-pickup-trucks-and-through-computer-screens/ |title = The Race Is On: Colorado’s 3rd District Candidates Stump From Pickup Trucks And Through Computer Screens|website=Colorado Public Radio |author = Kim, Caitlyn|date = 2020-08-24 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-12}}</ref>

===环境===
博伯特反对[[绿色新政|绿色新政]]。她声称，这项计划将耗资93万亿美元{{NoteTag|数字有争议。<ref>{{Cite web|last=McDonald|first=Jessica|date=2019-03-14|title=How Much Will the 'Green New Deal' Cost?|url=https://www.factcheck.org/2019/03/how-much-will-the-green-new-deal-cost/|access-date=2021-01-12|website=FactCheck|language=en-US}}</ref>}}，并导致美国破产。<ref name="CompCO07242020">{{cite news |last=Boebert |first=Lauren |date=2020-07-24 |title=Rifle restaurateur Lauren Boebert ready for a showdown in 3rd Congressional District |url=https://pagetwo.completecolorado.com/2020/07/24/rifle-restaurateur-lauren-boebert-ready-for-a-showdown-in-3rd-congressional-district/ |work=Complete Colorado – Page Two |location=Denver, Colorado|access-date=2021-01-12}}</ref>

===枪支权利===
博伯特是[[持枪权|枪支权利]]的支持者，她反对增加[[枪支管制|枪支管制]]法规<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-01|title=Lauren Boebert upsets 5-term congressman Scott Tipton in Colorado primary|url=https://www.pbs.org/newshour/politics/lauren-boebert-upsets-5-term-congressman-scott-tipton-in-colorado-primary|access-date=2021-01-12|website=PBS NewsHour|language=en-us}}</ref>。她反对[[科罗拉多州议会|科罗拉多州议会]]在2019年通过的科罗拉多州{{le|红旗法|Red flag law}}<ref name="Westworld01142020"/><ref name="heraldtimes"/>。

===保健===
博伯特呼吁废除由[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]总统签署成为法律的《[[患者保护与平价医疗法案|平价医疗法案]]》<ref>{{cite news |last=Paul |first=Jesse |date=2020-06-28 |title=Want to understand U.S. politics? Look at Colorado’s 3rd Congressional race |url=https://the-journal.com/articles/180040 |work=The Colorado Sun|location=Denver|access-date=2021-01-12}}</ref>。她不支持[[单一支付者医疗卫生系统|单一支付者医疗卫生系统]]，称这将使像她这样的小企业因为高昂的成本而倒闭<ref name="DurangoHear08162020">{{cite news |last=Hayes |first=Emily |date=2020-08-16 |title=Boebert rally in Cortez draws dozens concerned about individual liberty |url=https://durangoherald.com/articles/335506-boebert-rally-in-cortez-draws-dozens-concerned-about-individual-liberty |work=The Durango Herald|location=Durango, Colorado|publisher=Ballantine Communications, Inc. |access-date=2021-01-12 }}</ref>。

===移民===
博伯特支持修建[[美墨边界围栏|墨西哥-美国边境墙]]，反对特赦居住在美国的非法移民。<ref name="DetFP07012020">{{Cite web |url = https://www.freep.com/story/news/politics/elections/2020/07/01/scott-tipton-loses-lauren-boebert-colo-primary/5354122002/ |title = 5-term Rep. Tipton backed by Trump loses in Colorado primary, upset by businesswoman Lauren Boebert|website=Detroit Free Press |author =Cummings, William|date = 2020-07-01 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-12}}</ref>

