博伯特反对[[堕胎|堕胎]]，反对综合性[[性教育|性教育]]，反对联邦资助[[计划生育|计划生育]]。<ref name="heraldtimes" />

==个人生活==
博伯特和她的丈夫杰森·博伯特住在科罗拉多州[[锡尔特_(科罗拉多州)|锡尔特]]<ref name=discovers>{{Cite web|last=Stroud|first=John|title=Silt couple discovers that childbirth can be one wild ride|url=https://www.vaildaily.com/news/silt-couple-discovers-that-childbirth-can-be-one-wild-ride/|date=2009-07-20|access-date=2021-01-13|work=Vail Daily|language=en-US}}</ref>。在他们开餐馆之前，杰森·博伯特在油气田工作<ref name="auto"/>。他们有四个儿子<ref name=heraldtimes/>。劳伦·博伯特在2009年成为一名[[重生_(基督教)|重生基督徒]]<ref name=burgers/>。她第三个儿子是在丈夫开车去医院的途中在他们皮卡的前排座位生下的<ref name=discovers/>。

2010年，博伯特的邻居报警称她的[[比特犬|比特犬]]威胁他们的狗。博伯特因违反狗狗守则而被开罚单<ref name="dp 20200827">{{Cite news |last=Wingerter |first=Justin |date=2020-08-27 |title=Congressional candidate Lauren Boebert has a history of minor arrests, court no-shows |language=en-US |work=The Denver Post|url=https://www.denverpost.com/2020/08/27/lauren-boebert-arrests-colorado-3rd-mitsch-bush/ |access-date=2021-01-13}}</ref>。2015年，她在一个音乐节上被指控犯有{{le|轻罪|Misdemeanor}}和{{le|扰乱治安|Disorderly conduct}}，因为她告诉警官，他们逮捕一对[[合法饮酒年龄|未成年饮酒者]]是{{le|合宪性|Constitutionality|违宪}}的，因为这些青少年没有收到[[米兰达警告|米兰达警告]]<ref name="FMillerColoNewsL08132020">{{Cite web |url = https://coloradonewsline.com/2020/08/13/report-lauren-boebert-warned-arresting-deputies-she-had-friends-at-fox-news/ |title = Report: Lauren Boebert warned arresting deputies she had ‘friends at Fox News’|website=Colorado Newsline |author = Miller, Faith|date = 2020-08-13 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref>。根据副手们的报告，当她被铐上手铐时，博伯特试图避开警方，说“她在[[福克斯新闻|福克斯新闻]]有朋友”，这次逮捕将是“全国新闻”<ref name="FMillerColoNewsL08132020"/>。她两次未能出庭受审<ref name="FMillerColoNewsL08132020"/>。这一轻罪被撤销，因为[[梅萨县_(科罗拉多州)|梅萨县]][[地方检察官|地方检察官]]办公室认为陪审团不会判她有罪<ref name="FMillerColoNewsL08132020"/>。2016年，博伯特因驾驶不安全车辆而被传唤，她认罪<ref name="dp 20200827" /><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/26/us/colorado-lauren-boebert-congress.html |title =In Colorado, Fiery Political Novice Aims for a Seat in the House|website=New York Times |author = Hulse, Carl|date = 2020-09-26 |language = en|accessdate = 2021-01-13}}</ref>。

2021年1月13日，[[推特|推特]]以博伯特违反了其规定为由将博伯特的个人账户封锁到1月20日之后<ref>{{Cite web|last=Aedo|first=Zachary|date=2021-01-13|title=Rep. Lauren Boebert says Twitter account locked until Inauguration Day|url=https://krdo.com/news/2021/01/13/lauren-boeberts-twitter-account-locked-until-inauguration-day/|access-date=2021-01-15|website=KRDO|language=en-US}}</ref>。数小时后，推特解除了博伯特账户的封锁，称其员工“采取了不当的执法行动”<ref name="Canales">{{cite news |last1=Canales |first1=Katie |title=Twitter says it has reversed its 'incorrect' decision to lock Rep. Lauren Boebert's account |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/twitter-locks-boebert-account-pelosi-capitol-siege-2021-1 |access-date=2021-01-15 |work=Business Insider |date=2021-01-13}}</ref>。

